{"tid":807750,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(Rap經) Eminem-Kamikaze","createTime":"2018-09-05T18:53:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-09T19:56:06.000Z","uid":145395,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"865fc4570d85c697b9ee7e96216d8a96c7ee1032","tid":807750,"uid":145395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T18:53:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/06/014527_64e3742ae001aa743391beb309506e1d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F06%2F014527_64e3742ae001aa743391beb309506e1d.png&h=8a766e00&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n個album一出就成個down左落黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n然後聽第一首the ringer己經炮轟依加個新生hiphop圈搞到風氣十分差 唱埋d無意義既mumble rap<br />\n歌詞只有錢 女 雞 gang drugs violence <br />\n<br />\n除此之外好多人只係抄lil wayne既lazy rap style<br />\n其中中彈既有數位Lil字頭既rappers<br />\n仲有好單調到求其搵字都塞到入去既rap e.g Mxxxs<br />\n<br />\n其實佢又屌得冇錯 eminem既rap好多都有故事同清晣既topic 好多rappers都係受佢啟發 先推廣到依加咁多人聽rap<br />\n<br />\n相比起gucci gxxx果類 真係冇撚得比 同時佢亦都寸埋 Dxxxx 撈到風生水起全靠有班ghostwritters <br />\n又因爲比人寸佢回塘 大家都鐘意聽埋d 九唔搭柒既rap 所以好撚興<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n到我最期待果部分喇eminem向歌入面同machine gun kelly講你依加知自己有幾多斤兩啦傻閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n事源係下圖 (6年前eminem個女得16歲)<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/06/022408_9a7104af4d96363f2a9323df1f60802b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F06%2F022408_9a7104af4d96363f2a9323df1f60802b.png&h=5752ee6e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n就向兩日前第一個自殺者出現左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/4sNCyiyIc_8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F4sNCyiyIc_8&d=6fMU2XtVQY4ofq32ISlMYm6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=eac4ef2d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/4sNCyiyIc_8</a><br />\n雖然佢呢段diss係幾正（比起好多同期rappers佢skills係唔錯）<br />\n但係佢自己做錯事 5出聲咪算鳩數 今次還拖仲提人地前妻 聽完之後我覺得eminem應該想立即屌佢老母 所以十分期待呢條故事線既發展<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n聽完個album都知後續係5會咁簡單 本人覺得eminem應該上得神枱太耐 悶得滯就睇下有邊個傻閪忍唔住還擊 屌撚死佢地然後鞭屍解悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b72ed4363a210a49d65adf129e7325867f47673","tid":807750,"uid":145395,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T18:57:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8fd98c088548854c8b9d2df54e24b32ecbf97a5","tid":807750,"uid":145395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6b72ed4363a210a49d65adf129e7325867f47673","tid":807750,"uid":145395,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T18:57:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T20:52:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4719fe97e433e4691652e0e38b8b672207958a23","tid":807750,"uid":156511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T22:22:22.000Z","msg":"LM先<br />\n新碟仲煲緊未太啱口味<br />\n聽得最多Eminem仲係Curtain Call - The Hits"},{"pid":"57764837b980865797ce711b1104934c9c051de8","tid":807750,"uid":8359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"865fc4570d85c697b9ee7e96216d8a96c7ee1032","tid":807750,"uid":145395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T18:53:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/06/014527_64e3742ae001aa743391beb309506e1d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F06%2F014527_64e3742ae001aa743391beb309506e1d.png&h=8a766e00&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n個album一出就成個down左落黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n然後聽第一首the ringer己經炮轟依加個新生hiphop圈搞到風氣十分差 唱埋d無意義既mumble rap<br />\n歌詞只有錢 女 雞 gang drugs 